nodes.text: Frey Suun was a male Human Jedi Knight in the Jedi Order during the Clone Wars. He trained at the Jedi Temple, and dueled a Jedi Knight at one point. He wielded a blue-bladed lightsaber.

Like Florg Nerfherder, Frey Suun is a stand-in character in the game Clone Wars Adventures. He is also seen elsewhere in the game, training with his lightsaber under the eye of Jedi Master Luminara Unduli.
